    <description>Uses stock colors when custom colors are disabled</description>
    <description>Custom settings for when the switch is on and when it is off (connectivity module only)</description>
    <description>To apply settings simply expand the connectivity module</description>
		<description>Customize all the modules</description>
		<description>Customize the control center background, you can make it a gradient which you select four colors to make or a solid color you choose</description>
